╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  Tylluan — OPERATIONS MAP v1                                 ║
║  How things FLOW. What happens when you DO things.           ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

┌─ REQUEST FLOW: tylluan_do("list files in guilds/") ─────────┐
│                                                              │
│  Client                                                      │
│    │ POST /messages or GET /sse (MCP call_tool)             │
│    ▼                                                         │
│  transport/http/mod.rs → auth.rs (bearer check)             │
│    ▼                                                         │
│  transport/server/handlers.rs                                │
│    │ handle_kernel_tool("tylluan_do", args)                  │
│    ▼                                                         │
│  handler_do/routing.rs                                       │
│    │ 1. anchor_fast_path (keyword match, <1ms)              │
│    │ 2. BM25 scoring against catalog trigger_phrases        │
│    │ 3. pick best guild + best tool                         │
│    ▼                                                         │
│  registry/actor.rs → guild subprocess                       │
│    ▼                                                         │
│  guilds/builders/plugins/filesystem.py                       │
│    │ file_list(path="guilds/")                              │
│    ▼                                                         │
│  Result → MCP response → Client                            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ MEMORY FLOW ───────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  WRITE: tylluan_remember(content) → handler_remember.rs     │
│    embed BGE-M3 → SilvaDB node → auto_link edges → IVF     │
│                                                              │
│  READ: tylluan_recall(query) → handler_recall.rs            │
│    embed → BM25 + vector → RRF fusion → Jina rerank → top N│
│                                                              │
│  REASON: tylluan_think(query) → handler_think.rs            │
│    recall → BFS graph traversal → clusters → hub → analysis│
│                                                              │
│  GRAPH: tylluan_graph(command) → handler_graph.rs           │
│    add_triple | query_path | list_neighbors | stats | ppr   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ GUILD LIFECYCLE ───────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  BOOT:  tylluan.toml always_on → spawn → MCP handshake     │
│  LAZY:  first intent match → spawn → wait handshake → exec │
│  CRASH: supervisor detects → retry (max N) → FAILED if loop│
│  IDLE:  idle_suspend_secs → stop → respawn on next match   │
│                                                              │
│  Routing: router/catalog.rs (trigger_phrases per guild)     │
│  Adding:  1) .py in guilds/ 2) descriptor in catalog.rs    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ COMMON OPERATIONS ────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  BUILD:   cargo build -p tylluan-kernel                     │
│  CHECK:   cargo check -p tylluan-kernel                     │
│  TEST:    cargo test -p tylluan-kernel --lib                │
│  LINT:    cargo clippy -p tylluan-kernel -- -D warnings     │
│  FORMAT:  cargo fmt -p tylluan-kernel                       │
│  START:   ./tylluan-mcp.bat (Win) or ./tylluan-mcp.sh      │
│  HEALTH:  curl http://127.0.0.1:3030/health                │
│  GUILDS:  curl http://127.0.0.1:3030/api/v1/guilds         │
│  STOP:    Ctrl+C or taskkill /IM tylluan-nexus.exe /F       │
│                                                              │
│  TEST ROUTING:                                               │
│    curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:3030/api/v1/do \          │
│      -H "Content-Type: application/json" \                  │
│      -d '{"intent":"your intent"}'                          │
│                                                              │
│  MEMORY STATS (via MCP):                                     │
│    tylluan_graph(command="stats")                            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ ERROR RECOVERY ────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  "guild crash loop"  → check .py exists + pip deps + timeout│
│  "routing miss"      → adjust catalog.rs trigger_phrases    │
│  "502 from proxy"    → kernel not running, restart          │
│  "sqlite locked"     → two kernels running, kill all+restart│
│  "connection refused"→ use 127.0.0.1 not localhost          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
